1. *Bitka* je počela u zoru. (The battle began at dawn.)
2. Vođa je uzeo učešće u *bitci*. (The leader took part in the battle.)
3. Naši vojnici su izgubili *bitku*. (Our soldiers lost the battle.)
4. Pobedili smo u poslednjoj *bitci*. (We won the last battle.)
5. U *bitki* je korišćena nova tehnologija. (New technology was used in the battle.)
6. Ratnik je dobio mnogo rana u *bitki*. (The warrior received many wounds in the battle.)
7. Vojska se sprema za *bitku*. (The army is preparing for the battle.)
8. Kao gladijator, spreman sam za *bitku*. (As a gladiator, I am ready for the battle.)
9. *Bitka* za nezavisnost je bila teška. (The battle for independence was difficult.)
10. Rizikovao je svoj život u *bitki* za slobodu. (He risked his life in the battle for freedom.)

(Note: the star (*) indicates the use of the word "bitka" in each sentence.)